{"tid":1022844,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"克勤，麻煩您見到就入一入黎找找條尾數","createTime":"2019-02-15T10:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T01:50:59.000Z","uid":228758,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e935da93ed083c2a59bde7f23f8669f6d091f2","tid":1022844,"uid":228758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"小弟又獻醜了，最好有巴絲唱一唱助慶啦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推到找數　＋　ＭＶ　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n舊歡如夢(李克勤)<br />\n<br />\n專誠寫畀李克勤 毒撚有遺憾<br />\n今次隻歌係講佛 可否請您為我吟<br />\n＊般若般耶菠蘿蜜 萬般有緣份<br />\n(＊音:波喲波耶波蘿me)<br />\n今趟老兄願出力 功德充滿在社群<br />\n<br />\n喜逢知音唱經文 亦當顛倒眾生<br />\n諸訴四方話中淚 單身巴要互慰問<br />\n寶福山邊廟燒香 大煙惹愁恨<br />\n想您見到便笙歌 只得清唱願聽聞<br />\n<br />\n之前版本欠斯文 令一眾又遺恨<br />\n色相看穿萬千象 洗底請您別記恨<br />\n<br />\n汝等諸位枉拋磚 善因早扎根<br />\n只要戒色食齋禁慾 正經風氣定降臨<br />\n正經風氣定降臨 正經風氣定降臨"},{"pid":"3d494731906214e63791633440ab08b68a0b4fea","tid":1022844,"uid":92281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:05:12.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"5e37769378ec9b4c5a4d1afbe82cd9434385fe15","tid":1022844,"uid":40317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:06:04.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"841401228f4e0c538ef252eb2e9b68bac31701ea","tid":1022844,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"cd11bcc987c73a715b66d5fb997c107fa56553d7","tid":1022844,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"79befdaf0612f267ed73314d9a6007ce442cfdac","tid":1022844,"uid":176318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"d74f1ebd26f5b1d4c92e19eb6c3ef5ee3a547cca","tid":1022844,"uid":100720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"a952a2e2254f1559e0480df6afd80bbd135682f8","tid